title: Eastman M9000 CNC Fabric Cutting Machine
item_description:
Eastman M9000 CNC Fabric Cutting Machine

  • Manufacturer: Eastman
  • Model: M9000
  • Serial Number: T-00211
  • Voltage: 110 V
  • Width: 104”
  • Length: 420”
  • Height: 46.5”
  • Table Size: 72”W x 35’L
  • X-Axis Work Area: 36′
  • Y-Axis Work Area: 58.6″
  • Maximum Cutting Speed: 3600 IPM
  • Cut Accuracy: +-0.015″
  • Minimum Pneumatic Operating Pressure: 75 PSI

Removal Note: Item will be disconnected from power and air before removal date. The buyer of this lot will be fully responsible for disassembling and moving.

Control Unit Note: The control unit/computer included in this lot contains software to operate this machine. This software will not include the current owner's license and the buyer of this machine will need to purchase their own license. The software will remain installed on the control unit/computer.
